{"tid":1440090,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如 果 不 打 算 停 擺 機 場 ， 就 應 該 離 開 機 場 ！","createTime":"2019-08-10T10:31:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T10:47:02.000Z","uid":2565,"like":25,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"46cf96a825fe09e382bec43eb19649f3da6e8df2","tid":1440090,"uid":2565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:31:33.000Z","msg":"機場的確對香港經濟有極大影響，<br />\n但<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">如果不打算影響機場運作</span></strong>，<br />\n十萬人在機場與一百萬人在機場，<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">人數多少根本毫無分別</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n佔領區的一大弊病，<br />\n就是和理非認為自己出來了，<br />\n就是做對了事，<br />\n在佔領區裏賣弄感動，<br />\n就是得到了抗爭的成果。<br />\n機場只不過是販賣<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>「和理非贖罪卷」</strong></span>的地方，<br />\n<br />\n機場一直運作暢順，<br />\n香港現況並不會因為機場人數多少而改變。<br />\n而「和理非」與街頭「勇武」分頭行事，<br />\n將令運動走向衰敗。<br />\n<br />\n本人建議，<br />\n一、對香港政府作出更沉重的經濟打擊<br />\n二、返回街頭<br />\n<br />\n立即放棄<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>「機場很多人坐在地上，然後我們會成功」</strong></span>的荒謬想像。"},{"pid":"840f1faffe2fe5e1cbc7660bdb863a97bdaeb64e","tid":1440090,"uid":2565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:32:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"28575417f3cca233cae51f5eeb28efd104e65bdb","tid":1440090,"uid":92188,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:33:17.000Z","msg":"都係做3日，做埋先啦"},{"pid":"ffad23416ff1d3ac4b0b92b0b010225346da0a14","tid":1440090,"uid":2565,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:33:18.000Z","msg":"正評負評<br />\n說說你的理據"},{"pid":"bac7fb2699bf9c7559cbe46a72cb32ecaa83d940","tid":1440090,"uid":35924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28575417f3cca233cae51f5eeb28efd104e65bdb","tid":1440090,"uid":92188,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:33:17.000Z","msg":"都係做3日，做埋先啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:34:23.000Z","msg":"照做，但始終要有覺悟升級"},{"pid":"8400d51f69b73b5edbdb95d4e1e5cf977eba5ec3","tid":1440090,"uid":2565,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"28575417f3cca233cae51f5eeb28efd104e65bdb","tid":1440090,"uid":92188,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:33:17.000Z","msg":"都係做3日，做埋先啦"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:34:43.000Z","msg":"我只是擔心機場集會<br />\n會令勇武與和理非分道揚鑣"},{"pid":"300d2eb17fbee7cdf65d866d0f3d55fb3b3f833e","tid":1440090,"uid":76632,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:35:18.000Z","msg":"「機場很多人坐在地上，然後我們會成功」呢句我有保留。<br />\n<br />\n現場好多手足派緊傳單向大陛人及外國人宣傳香港人嘅信念及5大訴求，唔係人人都齋坐。"},{"pid":"d7d1278eee8f4b30123e542062a5ad3a3e51b479","tid":1440090,"uid":217441,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:36:07.000Z","msg":"做住先"},{"pid":"2b758d4bbc7bef57f0a72b4946431958ee14096c","tid":1440090,"uid":36478,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:37:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a180d263e708e8b30856432ab16f01b5c02cb7b2","tid":1440090,"uid":2565,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:37:38.000Z","msg":"所以政府態度會因為<br />\n「糟糕了，很多人在機場唱衰我們」<br />\n然後態度變軟？<br />\n我不認為。"},{"pid":"07c775264074aa95fe239cecde7f2d4440f6346e","tid":1440090,"uid":132611,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8400d51f69b73b5edbdb95d4e1e5cf977eba5ec3","tid":1440090,"uid":2565,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"28575417f3cca233cae51f5eeb28efd104e65bdb","tid":1440090,"uid":92188,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:33:17.000Z","msg":"都係做3日，做埋先啦"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:34:43.000Z","msg":"我只是擔心機場集會<br />\n會令勇武與和理非分道揚鑣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:37:41.000Z","msg":"最多咪搞埋聽日,下次又會再眾合返,再有人想搞多次機場先再提出討論比較好"},{"pid":"efb46a971d8411d7bb628a569af749c8070eb223","tid":1440090,"uid":53441,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:37:42.000Z","msg":"不分化 不割蓆"},{"pid":"059d85fa339fe0fc50eb4915edbdd2318a7861fa","tid":1440090,"uid":35005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:38:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zy6WL8g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzy6WL8g.jpg&h=3157dc6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">和理勇武 各自爬山</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"80fc6f8cfff79cf6847456d9d6fae8814cb5fa01","tid":1440090,"uid":9394,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:39:42.000Z","msg":"去機場的確唔需要咁多人坐 主要係派文宣or叫口號or 做人板會好啲<br />\n但講真出去遊行集會又可嘗唔係做了事 自我安慰呢<br />\n我唔係想割簾 所以運動我都支持<br />\n但既然不斷街頭抗爭都逼唔到出聲<br />\n去機場試下有咩問題 請唔好攻擊自己友"},{"pid":"0d16887af4a5bbff64c8d418a4e9e50ebbdb977c","tid":1440090,"uid":35005,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:40:22.000Z","msg":"9日前先叫人多啲入機場，<br />\n而家就叫人唔好入<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qiia0uK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQiia0uK.jpg&h=e44d8bfd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4c574e3a33c131fcd671389d326a61a71a9325c8","tid":1440090,"uid":31094,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:40:32.000Z","msg":"成大班屌機場，是人是鬼自己諗"},{"pid":"7c586f4ced374001f5af715bbf1e7b6ddf3e0f2a","tid":1440090,"uid":9394,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a180d263e708e8b30856432ab16f01b5c02cb7b2","tid":1440090,"uid":2565,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:37:38.000Z","msg":"所以政府態度會因為<br />\n「糟糕了，很多人在機場唱衰我們」<br />\n然後態度變軟？<br />\n我不認為。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:41:16.000Z","msg":"出去同狗開片確實係好多畫面 出好多汗水<br />\n但係咪代表效果好過機場和理非 <br />\n我都不認為"},{"pid":"514f68eb53caab38f1f8dc5268efd1c5c16025ff","tid":1440090,"uid":140326,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:41:32.000Z","msg":"咪再扮大台啦3毛<br />\n我地一早講好左<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">各有各做</span></span><br />\n手足想去邊自己決定"},{"pid":"c433c9cf51f07d49f03549c93bf0e71c5797785a","tid":1440090,"uid":135274,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a180d263e708e8b30856432ab16f01b5c02cb7b2","tid":1440090,"uid":2565,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:37:38.000Z","msg":"所以政府態度會因為<br />\n「糟糕了，很多人在機場唱衰我們」<br />\n然後態度變軟？<br />\n我不認為。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:42:20.000Z","msg":"所以政府態度會因為<br />\n「糟糕了，很多人在與黑警打游擊戰」<br />\n然後態度變軟？<br />\n我不認為。<br />\n<br />\n正如好多人係6.9之前都覺得大遊行係冇用，只係送香港最後一程，但冇6.9就唔會有6.12，冇6.12就唔會出現6.16，如此類推。<br />\n<br />\n我地需要既係信任，相信每一位手足。我地需要既係盡做，就算只有1%成功率都要做好件事。"},{"pid":"0efe745fb8efcbe34e869cf3a568e9333c8dc8bb","tid":1440090,"uid":170812,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:42:33.000Z","msg":"記唔記得71之前，和理非行左幾多次，先聚到咁多人響勇武後面打氣，攻破立法會？<br />\n<br />\n其實唔少人都知，癱瘓機場係一個核爆手段。而家攪多幾次和理非，等佢地習慣入機場，習慣響機場集會，咁到時勇武要升級，先有足夠back up。<br />\n<br />\n所以我係極支持現階段，係現階段，機場由和理非主打。"},{"pid":"bf8279a68833774a13d133f4d0db9801a4b114b6","tid":1440090,"uid":14026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:43:02.000Z","msg":"Right"},{"pid":"6daf8c6bb89a3ad7f5d10d37784b3a0375aac05f","tid":1440090,"uid":78666,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:44:32.000Z","msg":"分化撚D用語真係好明顯下"},{"pid":"177205049255e2f79ffbaa88b8d7c819c172066d","tid":1440090,"uid":44309,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8400d51f69b73b5edbdb95d4e1e5cf977eba5ec3","tid":1440090,"uid":2565,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"28575417f3cca233cae51f5eeb28efd104e65bdb","tid":1440090,"uid":92188,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:33:17.000Z","msg":"都係做3日，做埋先啦"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:34:43.000Z","msg":"我只是擔心機場集會<br />\n會令勇武與和理非分道揚鑣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:44:45.000Z","msg":"唔使擔心，唔會。各有各做。"},{"pid":"f48ce21f6ffea671be7639d725b0ceadf8260223","tid":1440090,"uid":282115,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:47:02.000Z","msg":"兄弟爬山<br />\n樣樣做<br />\n見機場人夠就轉場<br />\n自發既"}]}